(6476, 1, '2018-06-11 09:53:00', '2018-06-11 07:53:00', 'http://vimeo.com/236054374\n\nProduced my first talking action figure line with <a href="http://www.studiosophisti.nl/en/">Studio Sophisti</a> and <a href="http://www.happyworker.com/">Happy Worker</a> at <a href="https://www.achtung.nl/">Achtung! mcgarrybowen Amsterdam</a> for Adobe\'s Hovering Art Director campaign! The motion activated figures espouse sage advice, providing true art director feedback on any designer\'s work, whether requested or not.\n<img src="http://producedproductions.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Packaging_1.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6466" />\nAlso made a series of films, both in liveaction with production company <a href="http://www.hobbyfilm.com/">Hobby Film</a>: \nhttp://vimeo.com/236075667\nAs well as 3D animation with <a href="http://www.yumyumlondon.com/">Yum Yum London</a>:\nhttp://vimeo.com/236055696\nAnd a website with <a href="http://www.egotribe.nl/">Egotribe</a>, where designers could submit their favorite hovering art director comments for a change to win a doll:\nhttp://vimeo.com/236066725\nOh, and we turned the fake ginger beer ad from the film into a real bottled and branded softdrink with the help of print shop <a href="http://www.burocad.be/">Burocad</a>:\n<img src="http://producedproductions.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Adobe4.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6467" /> \n<img src="http://producedproductions.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Adobe_Stock_wolfbear.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6464" />\n\n', 'Hovering Art Director', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6461-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-06-11 09:53:00', '2018-06-11 07:53:00', '', 6461, 'http://producedproductions.com/6461-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
